column2:
- if you want a facet to be deployed to a new network (or if you want to request an update of a facet), write "latest" in the respective file (SC team will replace this info with the latest version number)
- if a facet is not supposed to be deployed to a certain network, write down a short reason (e.g. network not supported by bridge) and add grey background to the field (as shown in Example column)
- remember that immutable diamonds cannot be changed (i.e. no facets can be added). If you request a facet to be added to an immutable diamond, it will only be possible in the next release (i.e. when we redeploy the immutable diamond)
- please update the "Updated: <date>" information on every change so we keep track of when a facet (and its supported networks) was checked last
- please do not change any structure (e.g. merge/unmerge cells) of this file as it will be parsed by a script - please approach SC team if you need additional space for networks/facets
- copy/paste will often break the formatting. It is recommended to just enter text into cells manually. If you copy/paste, please make sure the formatting remains intact.
